      <title>越南股市因富时指数上调预期而出现 8 月以来最大涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/vietnamese-shares-rally-most-since-august-on-ftse-upgrade-hopes</link>
